Dependencies:

  brew install neovim/neovim/neovim
  brew install fzf
  brew install sourcekitten 
  brew install swiftlint 
  pip3 install neovim jedi flake8 pylint pyyaml
  pip2 install neovim pyyaml
  gem install neovim 
  stack install hlint ghc-mod

Installation:

  git clone git://github.com/alexmacedo/nvim-config.git ~/.config/nvim

Then, open editor `nvim` and execute `:PlugInstall`.
